自發佈以來，《寶可夢 皮卡丘》好評如潮，[[Game_Rankings|Game Rankings]]依據十五則評論給予遊戲85.47%的評分，這個使得本遊戲成為Game Boy第五位得分高以及所有遊戲第1017位得分高的遊戲<ref name="gr">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamerankings.com/gameboy/198314-pokemon-yellow-version-special-pikachu-edition/index.html |title=Pokemon Yellow Version: Special Pikachu Edition for Game Boy |publisher=GameRankings |date=1999-10-19 |accessdate=2010-10-12 |archive-date=2012-08-12 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69s7C8WzE?url=http://www.gamerankings.com/gameboy/198314-pokemon-yellow-version-special-pikachu-edition/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在滿分10分的制度下、《[[任天堂力量|任天堂力量]]》給了8分，[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]給了6.5分，[[Electric_Playground|Electric Playground]]給了7.5分。<ref name="gr"/>。《Sarasota Herald-Tribune》評道這對兒童來說是個好遊戲<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=NwodAAAAIBAJ&sjid=J34EAAAAIBAJ&pg=6670,899247&dq=pokemon-yellow+-neoseeker&hl=en |title=Sarasota Herald-Tribune - Google News Archive Search<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2017-01-11 |archive-date=2016-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160123214602/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=NwodAAAAIBAJ&sjid=J34EAAAAIBAJ&pg=6670,899247&dq=pokemon-yellow+-neoseeker&hl=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在一個由十名孩童組成的團體調查中，其中九名給出「很棒」或「傑出」的分數，但只有五位推薦購買<ref>[https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=dJ4sAAAAIBAJ&sjid=Wf0DAAAAIBAJ&pg=4814,520509&dq=pokemon-yellow+-neoseeker&hl=en Lakeland Ledger - Google News Archive Search<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>。[[IGN|IGN]]的Craig Harris讚賞了遊戲機制，他認為《皮卡丘》比《紅／綠》還要更好，並給出滿分評價<ref name="ign">{{cite web |author=Craig Harris |url=http://gameboy.ign.com/articles/162/162045p1.html |title=Pokemon Yellow: Special Pikachu Edition - Game Boy Review at IGN |publisher=Gameboy.ign.com |date=1999-10-19 |accessdate=2010-10-12 |archive-date=2012-06-26 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/68hvuUQiv?url=http://gameboy.ign.com/articles/162/162045p1.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。[[GameDaily|GameDaily]]的Chris Buffa將它列為最好的寶可夢遊戲之一，雖然只是個改良版，但還是有足夠的內容<ref>{{cite web|author= Chris Buffa |url=http://www.gamedaily.com/articles/galleries/best-and-worst-pokemon-games/?icid=aimDBDL2_link1-a&page=1&cp=8 |title=Gallery and Images |publisher=GameDaily |date=2008-08-26 |accessdate=2010-10-12}}</ref>。

除了讚譽以外、亦有不少評論家提出負面批評。[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]的Cameron Davis稱它只不過是個在《寶可夢 金／銀》推出之前安撫玩家的權宜之計，他評論「新的挑戰足以填補這段空窗期，但也只有這樣了。」<ref name="gs">{{cite web |last=Davis |first=Cameron |url=http://www.gamespot.com/gameboy/rpg/pokemonyellow/review.html?om_act=convert&om_clk=gssummary&tag=summary%3Bread-review |title=Pokemon Yellow Version: Special Pikachu Edition Review for Game Boy |publisher=GameSpot |date=1999-10-19 |accessdate=2010-10-12 |archive-date=2013-01-23 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20130123182040/http://www.gamespot.com/gameboy/rpg/pokemonyellow/review.html?om_act=convert&om_clk=gssummary&tag=summary;read-review |dead-url=yes }}</ref>[[AllGame|AllGame]]的Brad Cook評論，對於沒有玩過《紅／綠》的人、《皮卡丘》是不錯；不過如果玩過《紅／綠》的話，他建議等到《金／銀》推出<ref name="ag-review">{{cite web |last=Cook |first=Brad |url=http://www.allgame.com/game.php?id=20357&tab=review |title=Pokémon: Yellow Version - Special Pikachu Edition - Review |publisher=allgame |date=2010-10-03 |accessdate=2010-10-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141114211909/http://www.allgame.com/game.php?id=20357&tab=review |archivedate=2014-11-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[每日電訊報|每日電訊報]]》的Steve Boxer評論，雖然它的遊戲機制很不錯，但缺乏新的功能。並表示任天堂的手段貪婪，《皮卡丘》象徵著《寶可夢》在遊戲的道路上已經止步、並且轉變為一種行銷手法了。<ref>{{cite news |last=Boxer |first=Steve |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/reviews/4750738/Pokemon-Yellow.html |title=Pokémon Yellow |publisher=Telegraph |date=2000-06-08 |accessdate=2010-10-12 |location=London |archive-date=2014-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140225093204/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/reviews/4750738/Pokemon-Yellow.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

